<HEADLINE>Trial postponed</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>4</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>976765034</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
THE trial of Mrs Jill Thorley, former owner of Hillcrest retirement
home at Wigtown, who is accused of perjury at a fatal accident inquiry
